latestPosts.caption:
Do not forget to Save this for your Vietnam bucket list!📍🔥
🎥 Day 2 in Ha Long Bay, Vietnam 🇻🇳 which is all about luxury cruise, lushgreens and scenic views.
We booked a entire day tour✨Started with a pearl tour — Vietnam’s gem!
🏝️Next stop: beach break — we had option of swimming but we decided to hike for insane views ⛰️ and also didn’t carried our swimsuits🤪
🚣‍♀️Then came kayaking or boating we opted boating through postcard-perfect waters they stopped around so many points and the experience was amazing.
🌀Ended the day exploring massive tunnels with jaw-dropping carvings
Stayed the night in Ha Long and took the early morning flight to Da nang 🇻🇳
See you in  Danang the day 3 itinerary

Pro tip - Make sure to carry your food, the food served was wierd 🥲

latestPosts.caption:
🎥 Day 1 in Hanoi, Vietnam 🇻🇳
If you land at night then without sleeping head to the lively Beer Street 🍻
Then next morning  plan to go to the iconic Train Street 🚂
Explore the Ho Chi Minh Museum 🇻🇳
Then in the afternoon go to the Trang Tien for luxury shopping🛍
Then visit the stunning St. Joseph’s Cathedral ⛪️
By evening, Stroll around the peaceful Hoan Kiem Lake 🌿
Save this for your Hanoi trip! 📍
